name: jeffmod pac12 mod v2.2 *G5 Fix* (based on jeffmod v19a)
startingMessage: This is a mod that shuffles the 136 teams of jeffmod v19a to recreate the Pre-2022 Pac-12 with non-Pac-12 teams in their modern conferences with a few exceptions. All credit for jeffmod goes to nokieva. The only thing I did was lazily cut and paste their work. Original jeffmod notes: The number of bowls is for a 12 team playoff. This version needs to have FCCD ver 0.37.0 at a minimum. Have fun!
